snippet.title: Balatro - Friends of Jimbo (Pack 2) | Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
You still can't spell "collaboration" without "Balatro"

Add some visual flair to your decks with these new cosmetic card skins inspired by fan-favorite characters from Cyberpunk 2077, The Binding of Isaac, Slay The Spire, and Stardew Valley. This update is now available free of charge on PC, Consoles & Mobile

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2379780/Balatro/
